author: Ftanyos
title: Report: National Security Adviser Michael Flynn Resigns
text:
WASHINGTON (AP) — Embattled National Security Adviser Michael Flynn resigned Monday, according The Associated Press.
The resignation comes following reports that Flynn discussed U.S. sanctions with a Russian envoy before Trump’s inauguration.
Stay with CBSLA.com for more on this developing story.
